{"tid":1279783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家花十分鐘時間睇呢段片 睇下外國人係點樣睇我地哋做緊嘅事","createTime":"2019-07-02T18:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T13:38:38.000Z","uid":83371,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a540799598e603787d3a0b1fc9c4140cf5baedeb","tid":1279783,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"經過咗咁多日 世界各地都有好多報道<br />\n但都只係媒體去報道香港嘅事<br />\n或者報道當地支持嘅人有咩行動<br />\n但都好少會有街訪 去問一啲未必清楚成件事嘅外國人<br />\n呢一段片係新唐人電視台 New Tang Dynasty Television拍嘅<br />\n如果你唔知呢個台係咩料嘅 可以話你知 NTDTV 係美國最大嘅獨立非營利中文電視頻道<br />\n但係中共一直都封鎖同干擾呢個台 咁你大概知呢個台嘅立場<br />\n而呢一條片係訪問咗 new york 同 london 嘅人<br />\n當中有啲人一開始都唔太清楚香港其實發生咩事 <br />\n但主持解釋完條條例 政府嘅'回應' 再播埋啲警犬嘅暴行 啲外國人都好震驚<br />\n<br />\n另外有一個係古巴嘅叔叔 係經歷過社會主義嘅人 好明白我地嘅心情<br />\nLondon 有一個男人係2014年雨傘都係香港 佢都好為我地當時失敗咗而替香港人可惜<br />\n怕我地唔敢再發聲 但當佢知道我地今次嘅運動 係表示<span style=\"color: red;\">'it's lovely to see they actually turned out and protecting the freedoms the have from the govrnment'</span><br />\n一個澳洲女人 佢對8964嘅事歷歷在目 當知知香港發生緊呢一場抗爭 佢好怕天安門屠城會係香港重演 訪問其間停唔住眼淚 '<span style=\"color: red;\">because they'er trying to say something important  and they are not being heard and feel the answer will always be no from somewhere like China, they'er non negotiable.</span> 係佢嘅表情同語氣當中 你會感受到佢同我地一樣嘅憤慨同無力感<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多都好好 但唔特別 qoute 啦 一陣慢慢睇啦<br />\n我最希望大家睇埋最尾啲受訪者為香港打氣嘅說話<br />\nps:請忍耐一下個外國主持人係會講國語<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=08xPR755MPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D08xPR755MPI&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=91117824\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=08xPR755MPI</a>"},{"pid":"1fab5361dc3b515ec31b79e9940b253dd5c94735","tid":1279783,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8cc3562f610d00ac6b02f40b725000b19ae0a7d","tid":1279783,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"39c08433ff0aa90c6eae5e70888a836af686ece0","tid":1279783,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4527c23b10cb5b39d0c07d3260752ab6e91ca5c","tid":1279783,"uid":188969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"文宣既戰爭開始！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278390</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單文宣<br />\nSave低喜歡既圖，不停send俾人<br />\nShare 此link plzz </span></span>"},{"pid":"c1a673d84baf07c035e32b2ef9dc37b767052e93","tid":1279783,"uid":261998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:30:44.000Z","msg":"晏晝 FB 睇左，鬼佬比廢老更愛香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0afeeabc411884eba2253258dcdcf4eb92574e7","tid":1279783,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"推畀多啲人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f3a2c5bc925b6cc1ce24a5c3b927f5f57a7612","tid":1279783,"uid":83371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a673d84baf07c035e32b2ef9dc37b767052e93","tid":1279783,"uid":261998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:30:44.000Z","msg":"晏晝 FB 睇左，鬼佬比廢老更愛香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔單止愛香港 仲會為香港年輕人喊 膽心 可惜 <br />\n我地嘅社會就係需要咁嘅力量"}]}